New users can get Ether from bank accounts.

(before purchasing a product)
Buyer/Seller/Agent buys BTK from Escrow.
Buyer/Seller/Agent approves Escrow to spend a certain amount of BTK.

(when purchasing a product)
Same as the old escrow sequence.

example: https://ethereum.org/en/developers/tutorials/transfers-and-approval-of-erc-20-tokens-from-a-solidity-smart-contract/
